battlecode.common

Enum RobotType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RobotType>
      • battlecode.common.RobotType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RobotType>

    public enum RobotType
extends java.lang.Enum<RobotType>
    Enumerates the possible types of robots. More information about the capabilities of each robot type are available in the game specs. You can check the type of another robot by inspecting RobotInfo.type, or your own type by inspecting RobotController.getType().

    • Enum Constant Summary

      SOLDIER
